  "text": "The C term refers to total equilibrium concentrations at a certain temperature T, and C SA , surplus alkalinity, refers to the sum concentrations of all weak acid anions other than carbonic and boric acids. According to [CITATION_1] , respectively, whereas \u00f0C",
